abstract: >-
  K:BOT is a universal AI agent for the terminal with 39 specialist agents,
  228 tools, and 20 AI providers. It features an embedded llama.cpp inference
  engine, persistent memory, self-evolving capabilities, and local-first
  architecture. K:BOT covers every code ecosystem from your terminal —
  from research and VFX to audit, documentation, and open source contribution.
